# Serverless Media Processing Pipeline on AWS

## Business Problem
Global digital news org needed to ingest and process 10K+ media files/day from mobile reporters worldwide. Legacy EC2 solution couldn't handle spikes and cost $8K/month idle. Required <5 min processing time and 99.9% durability.

## Architecture Overview
Event-driven, serverless architecture for scalable media ingestion, validation, and processing. Decoupled with SQS + Step Functions for resilience.

